OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCoastal
OL,6,Fcloud will move inland through the
OL,7,Fevening giving a cloudy but dry night
OL,8,Facross much of the region. Isolated
OL,9,Flight rain possible in the far east.
OL,10,FWinds light and variable but breezy
OL,11,Falong the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA cloudy and dry start, sunny
OL,14,Fspells develop widely during the
OL,15,Fafternoon then turning clear
OL,16,Fovernight. Winds mainly light but
OL,17,Fbreezy along the coast. Around to just
OL,18,Fabove average temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
