OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FRemaining above average temperatures
OL,7,Fwith light winds. Variable amounts of
OL,8,Fcloud but plenty of sunny or clear
OL,9,Fspells. Most parts remaining dry
OL,10,Fthough an isolated shower can't be
OL,11,Fruled out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
